Class Address.Builder

java.lang.Object
hr.java.restaurant.model.Address.Builder
Enclosing class:
Address
public static class Address.Builder extends Object
The Builder class provides a flexible way to construct an Address object. It allows for incremental setting of the properties of the address and ensures immutability of the Address class.
